Simple
======

Put full filenames into config file.

Put partial filenames into config file.

Perform sanity checking against filenames.

Put TIFF filename from ImageJ and frame ranges into config file.

Put checksumming of pixel values into config file.

Perform check against checksumming

Allow restarting from GUI

Allow 3B to append to a file, rather than overwriting for a restart in place.



Complex
=======

Automatic chunking from GUI.

Reconstruct from multiple files.

Gridengine scheduling from GUI?

Simple job batching from GUI.
